cdata.name: PROVER
cdata.desc:
PROVER is a video content authenticator platform. It is an independent assistant that helps authenticate and verify video content. The platform was created to eliminate forgery of video materials, and confirm their authenticity. PROVER can work either as a stand-alone web/mobile app or as an integrated solution into 3rd party platforms using APIs and extensions.

The PROOF token is an Ethereum-based (ERC20) cryptocurrency. It is the token that powers the PROVER ecosystem as it grants access to its available goods and services.
